WE THOUGHT SHE WAS A MANATEE.

24:40.270 --> 24:41.635
Henry: WE HAVE ACT ED WICKEDLY.

24:41.640 --> 24:42.629
WE HAVE TURNED AWAY FROM YOUR

24:42.640 --> 24:43.641
GOOD LAWS.

24:43.650 --> 24:44.776
WHEN A MAN COMMITS ANY WRONG

24:44.780 --> 24:45.769
TOWARD A FELLOW MAN, THUS

24:45.780 --> 24:46.804
BREAKING WITH ADONAI, HE SHALL

24:46.810 --> 24:48.175
CONFESS TO WRONG HE HAS DONE.

24:48.180 --> 24:49.317
Matt: IT WAS A HIT AND RUN,

24:49.320 --> 24:50.309
HENRY!

