Matt: WE HAD MARIJUANA IN THE

24:56.320 --> 24:57.309
CAR--THAT'S 10 YEARS!

24:57.320 --> 24:58.321
Henry: NOBODY HAS TO KNOW ABOUT

24:58.330 --> 24:59.319
THAT.

24:59.330 --> 25:03.994
Matt: THEY'LL FIGURE IT OUT!

25:04.000 --> 25:06.161
WE DIDN'T KILL HER.

25:06.170 --> 25:07.262
THIS COULD ALL GO AWAY IF WE

25:07.270 --> 25:09.795
JUST KEEP IT COOL.

25:09.800 --> 25:10.801
Sean: WE HAVE TO KEEP A COOL

25:10.810 --> 25:11.799
HEAD HERE.

25:11.810 --> 25:12.799
Christian: YOU MAY BE

25:12.810 --> 25:14.072
COMFORTABLE WITH SECRETS--

25:14.080 --> 25:15.069
Sean: WHAT DOES THAT MEAN?

25:15.080 --> 25:16.069
Christian: BUT I'M NOT--WE HAVE

25:16.080 --> 25:17.206
TO TELL SOMEONE WHAT WE DID!

25:17.210 --> 25:18.199
Sean: ARE YOU FORGETTING PATIENT

25:18.210 --> 25:19.347
CONFIDENTIALITY, CHRISTIAN?

25:19.350 --> 25:20.817
Christian: OH, BULLSHIT!

25:20.820 --> 25:21.946
IF A PERSON IS A THREAT TO

25:21.950 --> 25:23.315
THEMSELVES OR OTHERS, THE POINT

25:23.320 --> 25:25.083
IS MOOT--WE'RE TURNING HIM IN!

25:25.090 --> 25:26.079
Henry: I DON'T CARE ABOUT JAIL.

25:26.090 --> 25:27.079
I'M TURNING US IN.

25:27.090 --> 25:28.079
Matt: WHOA. NO, YOU ARE NOT,

25:28.090 --> 25:29.352
HENRY. BE SMART.

25:29.360 --> 25:30.827
Sean: BE SMART, CHRISTIAN.

25:30.830 --> 25:31.819
WORD LEAKS TO THE MEDIA THAT WE

25:31.830 --> 25:32.819
TURNED HIM IN--

25:32.830 --> 25:33.819
Christian: ARE YOU DEFENDING

25:33.830 --> 25:34.819
THIS MONSTER?!

25:34.830 --> 25:36.354
Sean: I'M DEFENDING MY FAMILY.

25:36.360 --> 25:37.827
WORD TRAVELS FAST IN OUR

25:37.830 --> 25:38.819
LUXURIOUS CIRCLE.

25:38.830 --> 25:39.819
YOU KNOW THAT.

25:39.830 --> 25:40.831
PEOPLE SEE ON THE NEWS THAT WE

25:40.840 --> 25:41.829
BREACHED ETHICAL AGREEMENTS,

25:41.840 --> 25:42.829
AND THEN SUDDENLY OUR CUSTOMERS

25:42.840 --> 25:43.829
DON'T TRUST US WITH THEIR

25:43.840 --> 25:44.829
SECRETS, AND WE GO OUT OF

25:44.840 --> 25:45.829
BUSINESS!

25:45.840 --> 25:46.829
I HAVE A FAMILY TO SUPPORT.

25:46.840 --> 25:47.829
I HAVE 2 CHILDREN TO PUT THROUGH

25:47.840 --> 25:48.932
COLLEGE.

25:48.940 --> 25:50.805
Matt: WHAT ABOUT COLLEGE, HENRY?

25:50.810 --> 25:51.947
IF A POLICE RECORD KEEPS YOU OUT

25:51.950 --> 25:52.939
OF MEDICAL SCHOOL, WILL THE

25:52.950 --> 25:54.212
WORLD BE BETTER OFF?

25:54.220 --> 25:55.209
WE'RE NOT GOING TO THE POLICE.

25:55.220 --> 25:56.209
Christian: WE'RE GOING TO THE

25:56.220 --> 25:57.209
POLICE.

25:57.220 --> 25:58.209
Sean: AND WE'LL BE CALLED TO

25:58.220 --> 25:59.209
TRIAL AND THE CHURCH WITH THEIR

25:59.220 --> 26:00.209
BOTTOM LESS POCKETS WILL

26:00.220 --> 26:01.209
INVESTIGATE EVERY MISTAKE WE

26:01.220 --> 26:02.209
EVER MADE!

26:02.220 --> 26:03.209
YOU THINK LIZ WILL BE QUIET IN

26:03.220 --> 26:04.221
A ROOM FULL OF BLOODSUCKING

26:04.230 --> 26:05.219
LAWYERS?

26:05.230 --> 26:06.219
SHE'LL LEAD THEM STRAIGHT TO THE

26:06.230 --> 26:07.219
EVERGLADES, AND IT'S OFF TO

26:07.230 --> 26:08.219
PRISON WE GO!

26:08.230 --> 26:12.690
Christian: HE RAPED BOYS!

26:19.270 --> 26:21.101
Sean: WE HAVE TO DO SOMETHING.

26:21.110 --> 26:22.134
Henry: ISN'T--ISN'T YOUR DAD

26:22.140 --> 26:23.129
GONNA WORK ON HER FACE?

26:23.140 --> 26:25.847
I MEAN, ISN'T HE GONNA HELP US?

26:25.850 --> 26:26.999
Sean: WE'LL CALL THE DIOCESE AND

26:27.010 --> 26:28.272
TELL THEM WHAT WE DID,

26:28.280 --> 26:29.349
ANONYMOUSLY.

26:29.350 --> 26:31.238
Christian: YES...AND THEY'LL

26:31.250 --> 26:33.047
KICK HIM OUT AND REPORT WHAT HE

26:33.050 --> 26:34.415
DID TO THE POLICE.

26:34.420 --> 26:36.854
Sean: THEN IT'S THEIR PROBLEM.

26:36.860 --> 26:39.055
WE'LL BE OK.

26:39.060 --> 26:41.790
Matt: MY DAD'S VISITING HER

26:41.800 --> 26:42.698
TOMORROW.

26:47.900 --> 26:51.006
WE'RE GONNA BE OK.

27:19.200 --> 27:21.794
Kate: HELLO, MATT.

27:21.800 --> 27:23.461
Matt: HELLO.

27:23.470 --> 27:24.801
OH, MRS. FITZGERALD,

27:24.810 --> 27:26.061
THIS IS MY DAD.

27:26.070 --> 27:27.469
Kate: OH...

27:27.470 --> 27:28.300
Matt: HE'S A DOCTOR.

27:28.310 --> 27:31.074
Kate: HELLO, DR. MCNAMARA.

27:31.080 --> 27:33.469
Sean: SEAN.

27:33.480 --> 27:35.345
MATT TELLS ME YOU'RE DECLINING

27:35.350 --> 27:36.942
SURGERY FOR YOUR DAUGHTER.

27:36.950 --> 27:39.316
Kate: I'VE HIRED A PRACTITIONER,

27:39.320 --> 27:40.878
ONE OF THE BEST.

27:40.890 --> 27:42.710
THE ENVIRONMENT AT HOME IS MUCH

27:42.720 --> 27:44.824
MORE CONDUCIVE TO HEALING.

27:44.830 --> 27:47.481
WE'LL BE MOVING HER TOMORROW.

27:47.490 --> 27:48.957
Sean: MRS. FITZGERALD, YOUR

27:48.960 --> 27:49.892
DAUGHTER WAS IN A SERIOUS

27:49.900 --> 27:50.969
ACCIDENT.

27:50.970 --> 27:52.961
WITHOUT PLASTIC SURGERY, SHE'LL

27:52.970 --> 27:54.835
BE PERMANENTLY DISFIGURED.

27:54.840 --> 27:56.467
Kate: FALSE EVIDENCE APPEARING

27:56.470 --> 27:57.767
REAL.

27:57.770 --> 27:59.032
Matt: MRS. FITZGERALD, YOU CAN'T

27:59.040 --> 28:00.405
DO THIS TO HER.

