CARA WANTED TO FIT IN.

28:01.840 --> 28:02.909
YOU SAID SO YOURSELF.

28:02.910 --> 28:04.047
NOW, YOU KNOW HOW CRUEL--

28:04.050 --> 28:05.847
Kate: MATT...

28:05.850 --> 28:08.273
DR. MCNAMARA, I RESPECT YOUR

28:08.280 --> 28:11.408
BELIEF IN MATERIA MEDICA, PLEASE

28:11.420 --> 28:13.479
RESPECT MY RIGHT AS A PARENT TO

28:13.490 --> 28:14.957
DETERMINE MY DAUGHTER'S COURSE

28:14.960 --> 28:16.018
OF TREATMENT.

28:30.840 --> 28:33.729
Kate: PUT THAT DOWN.

28:36.880 --> 28:38.939
[SIGHS] DR. MCNAMARA, PLEASE...

28:38.950 --> 28:40.508
Sean: MRS. FITZGERALD, THE

28:40.510 --> 28:41.772
X-RAYS INDICATE THAT YOUR

28:41.780 --> 28:42.815
DAUGHTER SUFFERED SEVERAL

28:42.820 --> 28:44.014
FRACTURES WHICH ARE ENCROACHING

28:44.020 --> 28:45.282
ON THE OPTIC NERVE.

28:45.290 --> 28:47.087
Kate: WE'RE PRAYING TO HEAL

28:47.090 --> 28:48.057
THAT.

28:53.030 --> 28:54.156
Sean: WOULD YOU LIKE TO SEE

28:54.160 --> 28:55.855
IF YOUR PRAYERS ARE WORKING?

29:08.310 --> 29:10.175
MATT, WHY DON'T YOU WAIT FOR ME

29:10.180 --> 29:10.999
IN THE CAFETERIA?

29:11.010 --> 29:14.173
Matt: NO, UH, I'D LIKE TO STAY

29:14.180 --> 29:16.239
AND SUPPORT CARA.

30:00.360 --> 30:02.157
Sean: MRS. FITZGERALD, I'M VERY

30:02.160 --> 30:04.424
CONCERNED.

