Kate: OH, CARA.

30:11.370 --> 30:13.167
Sean: THE CHEEKBONE COMPRESSION

30:13.170 --> 30:14.876
HAS STOPPED BLOOD SUPPLY TO THE

30:14.880 --> 30:15.471
OPTIC NERVE.

30:15.480 --> 30:16.435
IF WE DON'T CORRECT THIS WITH

30:16.440 --> 30:17.202
SURGERY--

30:17.210 --> 30:18.245
Kate: NO.

30:18.250 --> 30:19.444
WE'LL PRAY HARDER.

30:19.450 --> 30:20.576
Sean: AS MUCH AS I SUPPORT YOUR

30:20.580 --> 30:22.013
