MRS. FITZGERALD, YOU HAVE TO LET

30:30.420 --> 30:32.126
ME OR MY EQUIVALENT AT THIS

30:32.130 --> 30:33.119
HOSPITAL OPERATE ON YOUR

30:33.130 --> 30:33.994
DAUGHTER.

30:34.000 --> 30:34.523
Kate: NO.

30:34.530 --> 30:35.656
THIS IS AN ILLUSION.

30:35.660 --> 30:36.627
PLEASE LEAVE.

30:36.630 --> 30:37.619
Sean: IF YOU DON'T AGREE TO LET

30:37.630 --> 30:38.562
ME OPERATE ON YOUR DAUGHTER--

30:38.570 --> 30:39.320
Kate: YOU'LL WHAT?

30:39.330 --> 30:40.661
REPORT ME, DR. McNAMARA?

30:40.670 --> 30:41.489
TO WHOM?

30:41.500 --> 30:42.660
Sean: I'LL HAVE NO CHOICE BUT TO

30:42.670 --> 30:44.137
SUBMIT AN IMMEDIATE PETITION AND

30:44.140 --> 30:46.005
TAKE MEDICAL CUSTODY OF CARA.

30:46.010 --> 30:49.400
Kate: YOU WON'T DO THAT.

30:49.410 --> 30:51.401
I LOVE MY DAUGHTER.

30:51.410 --> 30:52.968
YOU CAN SEE THAT.

30:52.980 --> 30:55.278
YOU WON'T DO THAT.

31:09.160 --> 31:11.128
Christan: SO, SINCE WE HAVE

31:11.130 --> 31:12.324
MEDICAL CUSTODY, DOES THAT MEAN

31:12.330 --> 31:14.059
WE HAVE TO PAY FOR HER COLLEGE?

