SERIOUSLY, WHAT HAPPENS AFTER WE

31:17.200 --> 31:18.167
PATCH THIS PUMPKIN?

31:18.170 --> 31:19.398
Sean: WE'RE NOW LEGALLY BOUND TO

31:19.410 --> 31:21.037
SUPERVISE THE OPERATION AND HER

31:21.040 --> 31:22.109
RECUPERATION.

