31:33.050 --> 31:34.187
HOOD WITH ME ONCE IN A WHILE,

31:34.190 --> 31:35.009
DON'T YOU THINK?

31:35.020 --> 31:36.009
I GAVE HIM THE OPTION.

31:36.020 --> 31:36.952
HE WAS INSISTENT.

31:36.960 --> 31:37.710
Christan: I DON'T RECALL MATTY

31:37.720 --> 31:39.051
EVER TALKING ABOUT THIS GIRL.

31:39.060 --> 31:40.482
Sean: ME, NEITHER, BUT I'M PROUD

31:40.490 --> 31:41.320
OF HIM.

31:41.330 --> 31:42.524
HE'S BEEN SO COMPASSIONATE ABOUT

31:42.530 --> 31:43.292
HER.

31:43.300 --> 31:44.221
ACTUALLY, IF HE DIDN'T GET

31:44.230 --> 31:45.367
INVOLVED WHEN HE DID, SHE WOULD

31:45.370 --> 31:47.326
HAVE GONE BLIND.

31:51.610 --> 31:53.100
Christan: DID YOU CALL THEM,

31:53.110 --> 31:54.270
THE DIOCESE?

31:54.280 --> 31:55.269
Sean: GOT A MACHINE.

31:55.280 --> 31:56.201
Christan: WELL, DID YOU LEAVE A

31:56.210 --> 31:56.733
MESSAGE, THOUGH?

31:56.740 --> 31:57.672
Sean: WE'RE DOING THIS

31:57.680 --> 31:58.749
ANONYMOUSLY, CHRISTIAN,

31:58.750 --> 32:01.014
REMEMBER?

32:01.020 --> 32:02.271
Christan: IT IS SO SHOCKING TO

32:02.280 --> 32:03.417
ME, PARENTS' DISREGARD FOR THEIR

32:03.420 --> 32:05.047
CHILDREN'S WELLBEING:

32:05.050 --> 32:07.041
HER MOTHER, DEVON GRECO'S

32:07.050 --> 32:10.713
FATHER.

