Devon: MAY I HELP--

32:26.170 --> 32:27.432
Christan: I SAW ON YOUR PATIENT

32:27.440 --> 32:29.203
FORM THAT YOU OWNED YOUR OWN

32:29.210 --> 32:32.441
FLOWER STORE.

