YOU SHOULD PUT THOSE IN WATER.

33:06.210 --> 33:07.472
LOOK, I DIDN'T MEAN TO BE RUDE

33:07.480 --> 33:08.242
TO YOU.

33:08.250 --> 33:11.219
Devon: YEAH.

33:11.220 --> 33:13.017
WELL, YOU WERE.

33:17.220 --> 33:18.289
Christan: HEY, I JUST SENT YOU

33:18.290 --> 33:19.689
FLOWERS.

33:19.690 --> 33:22.352
GIMME A BREAK.

33:22.360 --> 33:24.191
AND I'LL GIVE YOU ONE.

33:24.200 --> 33:25.827
Devon: YOU'LL GIVE ME A NOSE

33:25.830 --> 33:27.161
JOB?

33:27.170 --> 33:30.560
Christan: YEAH.

