I HAVE HIS HANDS, TOO, AND ONE

33:55.600 --> 33:57.591
TOE ON MY LEFT FOOT.

33:57.600 --> 33:58.624
I REALIZED, WHAT WAS I GONNA DO,

33:58.630 --> 34:00.791
MAKE OVER MY ENTIRE BODY?

34:00.800 --> 34:01.732
IF I DID THAT, HE'D STILL BE

34:01.740 --> 34:04.800
WINNING.

