IT WAS NEVER GONNA BE OVER...

34:06.840 --> 34:11.140
UNTIL I MADE IT BE OVER.

34:11.150 --> 34:15.541
SO I LOOKED HIM UP.

34:15.550 --> 34:17.142
Christan: DID YOU GET WHAT YOU

34:17.150 --> 34:18.139
NEEDED?

34:22.290 --> 34:23.814
Devon: THAT ONLY HAPPENS IN TV

34:23.820 --> 34:27.824
MOVIES.

34:27.830 --> 34:31.288
HE JUST KEPT CRYING IN HIS

34:31.300 --> 34:35.191
CRAPPY STUDIO APARTMENT

34:35.200 --> 34:38.567
AND SAYING HE WAS SORRY.

34:38.570 --> 34:41.630
HE WAS SICK.

34:41.640 --> 34:44.245
HE COULDN'T CONTROL IT.

34:47.580 --> 34:50.515
I THOUGHT I WOULD CRY

34:50.520 --> 34:53.512
AND RAGE AND...

34:53.520 --> 34:55.511
GET IT ALL OUT...

35:01.730 --> 35:03.652
