35:08.740 --> 35:11.538
I FELT...NOTHING.

35:20.750 --> 35:21.739
Christan: WHAT WOULD YOU HAVE

35:21.750 --> 35:24.389
DONE IF HE WAS DEAD AND YOU

35:24.390 --> 35:26.483
NEVER...

35:26.490 --> 35:28.253
GOT TO CONFRONT HIM?

35:30.620 --> 35:32.429
Devon: WHY DO YOU ASK?

35:35.760 --> 35:36.920
Christan: IT'S JUST GOOD THAT

35:36.930 --> 35:38.295
YOU GOT TO DEAL WITH HIM AND

35:38.300 --> 35:40.518
WHAT HE DID BEFORE HE DIED.

35:42.500 --> 35:45.628
Devon: YEAH. WELL...

35:45.640 --> 35:48.370
WON THE BATTLE, LOST THE WAR.

35:48.380 --> 35:51.508
EVEN WHEN HE DIES, THERE'LL BE A

35:51.510 --> 35:52.875
DOZEN OTHER BASTARDS RISING UP

35:52.880 --> 35:55.644
TO TAKE HIS PLACE...

35:55.650 --> 35:59.484
AND, JUST LIKE HIM, THEY'LL GET

35:59.490 --> 36:01.310
AWAY WITH IT.

