Shannon: THANK YOU.

36:11.330 --> 36:12.524
THANK YOU VERY MUCH FOR COMING.

36:12.530 --> 36:13.497
YOU HAVE GOOD TIME?

36:13.500 --> 36:14.535
YOU DID GOOD TODAY.

36:14.540 --> 36:15.393
YOU DID.

36:15.400 --> 36:15.968
YOU DID VERY WELL.

36:15.970 --> 36:17.369
I WAS VERY PROUD OF YOU.

36:17.370 --> 36:18.906
IT WAS NICE.

36:18.910 --> 36:21.231
AND NEXT WEEK, YOU'LL BE BACK?

36:21.240 --> 36:22.309
