36:22.310 --> 36:24.346
ALL RIGHT, THAT'LL BE FUN.

36:47.300 --> 36:48.961
Sean: HOW DO YOU FEEL?

36:48.970 --> 36:52.303
Megan: HUNG OVER.

36:52.310 --> 36:53.561
NERVOUS.

