I'M SORRY I NEVER NOTICED YOU

37:41.320 --> 37:42.958
BEFORE AT SCHOOL.

37:47.760 --> 37:50.957
AND I'M SORRY YOU FELT SO ALONE.

38:04.380 --> 38:07.304
I DID THIS TO YOU, CARA.

38:10.520 --> 38:12.442
IT WAS ME.

38:17.790 --> 38:20.452
AND I'M SO SORRY.

38:23.400 --> 38:25.595
I'M SO SORRY.

