Sean: NOT YET.

38:51.690 --> 38:53.021
LOOK, IF I CAN'T GET SOMEONE ON

38:53.030 --> 38:54.725
THE PHONE BY 5:00, WE'LL COME UP

38:54.730 --> 38:55.958
