38:55.960 --> 38:57.427
Christan: DON'T WORRY, SEAN.

38:57.430 --> 38:59.921
I'LL TAKE CARE OF IT.

39:21.460 --> 39:24.725
Shannon: GOOD AFTERNOON.

39:24.730 --> 39:26.789
