Christan: I'VE LOST MY FAITH,

39:42.540 --> 39:43.529
FATHER.

39:43.540 --> 39:46.873
I'VE DRANK.

39:46.880 --> 39:49.212
I'VE DONE DRUGS.

39:49.220 --> 39:51.176
I'VE FORNICATED WITH WOMEN AND

39:51.180 --> 39:54.718
DISCARDED THEM LIKE TRASH.

39:54.720 --> 39:56.950
I'VE LOST MY SOUL.

40:00.160 --> 40:04.028
THE BOYS YOU RAPED WILL BE

40:04.030 --> 40:04.962
SAYING THE SAME THING IN 20

40:04.970 --> 40:06.062
YEARS.

40:06.070 --> 40:09.164
DID YOU KNOW THAT?

40:15.910 --> 40:17.639
Shannon: I KNOW THAT AS A PARENT

40:17.640 --> 40:19.904
OF ONE OF MY ACCUSERS, IT'S HARD

40:19.910 --> 40:21.241
TO LOOK AT YOUR OWN CHILD AND

40:21.250 --> 40:23.775
ACCEPT HIS LYING.

40:23.780 --> 40:25.816
CHILDREN MAKE UP STORIES.

40:25.820 --> 40:28.550
Christan: I'M NOT A PARENT.

40:28.560 --> 40:30.778
I'M YOUR PLASTIC SURGEON,

40:30.790 --> 40:33.520
MICHAEL.

40:33.530 --> 40:34.554
REMEMBER ME?

40:43.540 --> 40:44.905
Shannon: I'VE STOPPED.

40:44.910 --> 40:48.209
I WAS SICK, AND I'VE STOPPED.

40:48.210 --> 40:49.507
I HAVEN'T TOUCHED ANYONE IN 2

40:49.510 --> 40:50.499
YEARS.

40:50.510 --> 40:51.909
Christan: IS THIS A CONFESSION,

40:51.910 --> 40:53.275
FATHER?

40:53.280 --> 40:55.214
Shannon: I'VE REPENTED IN MY OWN

40:55.220 --> 40:59.088
WAY.

40:59.090 --> 41:00.546
GOD DOESN'T JUDGE.

41:00.550 --> 41:01.687
WHY DO YOU?

41:01.690 --> 41:04.113
Christan: ARE YOU READY TO MAKE

41:04.120 --> 41:06.953
A CON FESSION, FATHER?

41:06.960 --> 41:08.222
Shannon: I HAVE TO LIVE WITH IT.

41:08.230 --> 41:09.697
I'VE DONE BETTER.

41:14.230 --> 41:16.266
WHEN DOES IT STOP?

41:16.270 --> 41:18.067
Christan: ARE YOU READY TO MAKE

41:18.070 --> 41:20.038
A CON FESSION, FATHER?

41:34.020 --> 41:35.009
Shannon: ARGHHH...

41:35.020 --> 41:37.250
Christan: MAKE YOUR CONFESSION.

41:37.260 --> 41:38.625
YOU CALL THE POLICE AND MAKE

41:38.630 --> 41:39.881
YOUR CONFESSION, OR I WILL LEAVE

41:39.890 --> 41:41.221
YOU HERE TO BLEED OUT.

41:41.230 --> 41:44.688
I KNOW JUST WHICH ARTERY TO CUT.

41:44.700 --> 41:46.565
Shannon: I CAN'T.

41:46.570 --> 41:48.663
I'M AFRAID.

41:48.670 --> 41:49.659
IF I GO TO PRISON, THEY'LL KILL

41:49.670 --> 41:50.261
ME.

41:50.270 --> 41:51.567
Christan: DID YOU REALLY THINK

41:51.570 --> 41:52.867
YOU'D GET AWAY WITH IT?

41:52.870 --> 41:54.007
Shannon: THERE WAS NO OTHER WAY.

41:54.010 --> 41:56.638
AFTER ALL, AREN'T YOU IN THE

41:56.640 --> 41:59.609
BUSINESS OF LIES?

41:59.610 --> 42:00.577
[SCREAMS]

42:02.750 --> 42:06.015
I WANT TO STOP.

42:06.020 --> 42:07.612
I DO.

42:07.620 --> 42:08.882
[PANTING]

42:08.890 --> 42:12.758
BUT WHEN I SEE THE BOYS...

42:12.760 --> 42:14.250
I FEEL THINGS.

42:18.630 --> 42:23.761
OH...GOD!

42:23.770 --> 42:25.101
FORGIVE ME.

42:29.040 --> 42:30.837
I WANT THEM.

42:36.120 --> 42:38.918
Christan: I HAVE PICTURES.

42:38.920 --> 42:41.081
YOU WANT REDEMPTION?

42:41.090 --> 42:43.183
TURN YOURSELF IN.

42:43.190 --> 42:44.782
EITHER WAY, YOU'RE GOIN' TO

42:44.790 --> 42:45.779
JAIL.

42:45.790 --> 42:47.985
WHETHER YOU GO TO HELL IS UP TO

42:47.990 --> 42:48.593
YOU.

43:11.080 --> 43:12.286
Shannon: ALL RIGHT.

43:48.720 --> 43:49.948
Sean: CHRISTIAN, WHAT HAVE YOU

43:49.960 --> 43:51.382
DONE?

43:51.390 --> 43:52.926
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

43:57.130 --> 43:59.826
Christan: I CAN'T DO IT, SEAN.

43:59.830 --> 44:01.263
Sean: YOU CAN'T DO WHAT?

44:01.270 --> 44:04.728
Christan: I'VE BEEN PRAYING...

44:04.740 --> 44:08.062
TO FORGIVE, BUT I CAN'T DO IT.

44:11.140 --> 44:12.175
Sean: THE AUTHORITIES WILL DEAL

44:12.180 --> 44:13.738
WITH HIM NOW.

44:13.750 --> 44:15.274
Christan: NOT HIM.

44:18.020 --> 44:19.942
ME.

44:26.760 --> 44:28.819
Sean: WHAT DID YOU DO?

44:36.170 --> 44:39.162
Christan: I LET HIM TOUCH ME.

44:39.170 --> 44:43.903
FOR YEARS, I LET HIM TOUCH ME.

44:43.910 --> 44:46.743
Sean: WHO?

44:46.750 --> 44:48.445
Christan: MR. TROY.

44:48.450 --> 44:51.749
YOUR FOSTER FATHER?

44:51.750 --> 44:53.149
HE'S DEAD, AND I THOUGHT

44:53.150 --> 44:54.185
THAT WOULD END IT,

44:54.190 --> 44:56.351
BUT IT DIDN'T.

45:00.190 --> 45:02.055
Sean: CHRISTIAN, YOU WERE JUST A

45:02.060 --> 45:05.928
BOY.

45:05.930 --> 45:09.229
IF HE ABUSED YOU...

45:09.240 --> 45:12.300
IT WAS HIS FAULT.

45:12.310 --> 45:16.929
HE HAD THE POWER.

45:16.940 --> 45:18.942
HE'S THE ONE.

45:21.210 --> 45:22.768
Christan: I DIDN'T HAVE ANYTHING

45:22.780 --> 45:25.988
WHEN HE TOOK ME IN.

45:25.990 --> 45:29.915
I WANTED TO BE...SOMEBODY.

45:35.960 --> 45:37.097
HE SAID HE'D GIVE ME MONEY

45:37.100 --> 45:42.367
IF I LET HIM TOUCH ME.

45:42.370 --> 45:43.894
AND I DID.

45:47.240 --> 45:48.969
I BOUGHT THINGS.

45:53.110 --> 45:56.375
I SOLD MYSELF.

45:56.380 --> 45:58.109
OH...

45:58.120 --> 46:00.384
OH, GOD...

46:00.390 --> 46:02.915
I SOLD MYSELF.

46:06.130 --> 46:08.519
OH, GOD.

46:08.530 --> 46:10.191
OH, GOD.

46:29.280 --> 46:30.144
[CAPTIONED BY THE NATIONAL

46:30.150 --> 46:31.139
CAPTIONING INSTITUTE

